About Us

ZAGG Brands is a global leader in accessories and technologies that empower mobile lifestyles. Our award-winning product portfolio includes screen protection, power management solutions, mobile keyboards, cases and personal audio. Regardless of our success, ZAGG Brands remains a scrappy, entrepreneurial company at heart that seeks to earn your trust every day.

Woman taking a picture

Live Fearlessly

InvisibleShield is the industry standard and #1 selling mobile screen protector. As the original category creator of mobile screen protection, we provide premium, lifetime protection for mobile device screens against shattering or scratching through military-grade solutions. Every day, we provide peace of mind and empower people to enjoy their mobile devices fearlessly.

iPhone X charging on a wireless charging base

Power for All

mophie, the #1 selling battery case manufacturer and the #1 external battery brand in the US, is a California-based, award-winning designer and manufacturer that empowers the mobile world to Stay Powerful. Widely acclaimed for innovative mobile solutions, mophie is the proud developer of the original juice pack. mophie products are recognized for style and engineered for performance, providing a seamless integration of hardware, software and design.

Someone using a tablet with a ZAGG keyboard

Life Unleashed

ZAGG is driving the mobile lifestyle forward with products that allow customers to be productive and connected at work and at play. Our products free people from the confines of the traditional workplace and make it so “getting away” doesn’t mean being disconnected. We support the communicators, commuters, and creators who live a life unleashed.

A man putting a Braven earbud into his ear

Toughest, Most Talented Audio on the Planet

Audio geniuses by profession, outdoor adventurists by passion: BRAVEN creates high-end sound that can go anywhere, empowering people to bravely explore the great outdoors. Our products are field-tested in the Rocky Mountains and intensify every outdoor experience from biking down mountains to jumping into a lake after a trail run. We celebrate bravery and pushing beyond personal limits.

Girl listening to music

Sound of Freedom

IFROGZ believes everyone deserves high quality headphones and earbuds. That’s why we took what’s good in audio—like dual drivers, wireless control features, water-resistance and noise-reduction—and removed all the extras that needlessly drive up the price, like the hype and celebrity endorsements. Now, rich sound is accessible to everyone.

Someone holding a phone with a Gear4 case

Ultimate Impact Protection

Gear4 is the #1 impact protection case brand in the U.K. Our tough, stylish cases feature D3O®, the market-leading impact protection material. Now established in over 40 countries, Gear4 has satisfied millions of consumers world-wide who demand reliable protection and upscale design. We meet the impeccable standards of British engineering and innovation and deliver unique, well-designed products that protect your most precious devices.

Halo Bolt

Power Your Life

HALO designs and develops clever, innovative products that make consumers’ lives easier. As the influence of consumer electronics continues to grow, HALO’s goal is to continually ensure that the accessories you pair with these everyday products are not only practical but aesthetically pleasing. Everyone deserves reliable solutions that also reflect their unique taste.

About Us – Network Outfitters

Simply put, Network Outfitters is the fastest, easiest way to get the new, refurbished or pre-owned networking equipment you need at the best possible price. Guaranteed. But that’s just part of the story.

DR4001103-E6 FrontOur founder, Kurt Rawlings has been in the networking industry since 1987.

From 1987 – 2000 Kurt was the Co-Owner and VP of sales and marketing at Computer Recyclers in Utah.

Computer Recyclers was a pioneer in it’s day to start the Ecycling movement.

After several years and many lessons learned, Kurt Rawlings founded Network Outfitters in 2000 because he saw an increased opportunity to provide better value and better service than the market was currently offering.

And it’s working. Our business has grown year over year. That’s because we treat our customers the way we’d want to be treated. Our customers, in turn, have rewarded us through their repeat business and referrals.

We’re able to do what we do because the market for networking equipment is unique. For one thing, pre-owned and refurbished equipment represents an enormous cost savings compared to new, and it is generally unavailable from the manufacturers or their VARS. Not only are we able to provide a lower cost alternative, we can do so without the typical lead times and with much stronger warranty programs than buying direct.

Also, the market for this equipment is fragmented. It can be difficult, time-consuming and often impossible for systems integrators, IT consultants, network architects, government or education network support professionals, and end users to locate needed hardware, let alone a reputable supplier.

ft-logoThat’s where we come in. Through our many combined years in the industry, we’ve developed an extensive source network for pre-owned, refurbished and new networking equipment. Our products are thoroughly tested, backed by an industry leading warranty, and, more importantly, you’ll always know where to find us after the sale. Why spend days or weeks tracking down the hardware you need and gamble on the quality and reliability of the equipment and the vendor? Chances are we have it in stock or can source it for immediate shipment. And we’ll guarantee the quality, and get it to you at a much better price than you could find on your own.

Finally, we understand the importance of network continuity and realize that downtime is simply not acceptable. We’ve made it our mission to place our customers’ needs first. Our automated processing enables us to expedite orders tailored specifically to your delivery requirements. We process final invoices and provide tracking information before you ever have a chance to wonder about the status of your order. In this dynamic business, your needs can change in an instant. Our talented and intuitive staff is ready and willing to adapt on the fly to ensure you’re satisfied with the products and the service you receive from us.

Though our company has grown over the years, we’re still here every day, ensuring that our sales staff delivers the high standard of customer service we established ourselves from day one. And even though we have fancy job titles on our business cards now, we’re not above personally taking phone orders or sending out quotes. At Network Outfitters, customer service is part of everyone’s job description.


When you are looking for new, pre-owned, or refurbished networking equipment from any of  the  major manufactures, you deserve an easy, hassle-free shopping experience. Our goal is simple: deliver maximum value, impress you with our service, and earn your repeat business.

Whether you request a quote online, or call us directly, our goal is to get you the pricing and availability information you need within 30 minutes or less. Usually, that means 15 minutes or less.

Not sure what you need? Our responsive sales staff is experienced in networking infrastructure and product compatibility. From the latest technologies, to second generation and end-of-life parts, we’ll work to help you identify a solution and get it to you at the best possible price.


Systems integrators, IT consultants, network architects, government or education network support professionals and end users can count on Network Outfitters to provide reliable, application tested, top quality products.


Looking for a router, switch, network security hardware, wireless equipment, content or access server, or VOIP telephony? We handle new, refurbished and pre-owned networking equipment from Cisco, HP, Foundry, Juniper, 3COM, Nortel and all other major manufacturers.
